skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: d. c. life
des:
Welcome to Washington, D.C. Life! You can explore the various lifestyles of D.C.’s luxurious and trendy communities. You can also query about real estate agents, popular restaurants, the ideal time to put your house on the market, get local walk scores and get information on local restaurants. 

Once you enable the skill, you can ask a variety of questions such as:

- What is the best area in D.C. to purchase a condo?
- When was Georgetown established?
- What is the walk score of Logan Circle?
- When is the best time to put my house on the market?
- Where is the best pizza restaurant?
- Looking for bakery in Georgetown

At the end of an Alexa presented answer, you will have the option to receive a text with pertinent information via weblink. This makes it convenient to keep information on your smartphone for future reference.
